## Key Conventions

- **Controllers use single-action classes** named after the HTTP verb they serve (`IndexAction`, `StoreAction`, `UpdateAction`, `DestroyAction`, etc.), grouped in folders by resource.
- **Roles**: Two main roles — `admin` and `professional`. Guards are `EnsureAdmin` and `EnsureProfessional` middleware.
- **Frontend pages** mirror backend controllers: a page in `resources/js/pages/patients/` corresponds to `app/Http/Controllers/Patient/`.
- **Types** are centrally defined in `resources/js/types/` and re-exported from `index.ts` files — always import from the nearest index.
- **shadcn/ui components** live in `resources/js/components/ui/` and should not be edited directly; extend them via wrapper components.
- **AI feature (Kosmo)**: Backend logic in `app/Services/KosmoService.php` and `app/Models/KosmoBriefing.php`; frontend in `resources/js/pages/kosmo/` and `resources/js/components/kosmo/`.
